Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:32.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur3}吧吧吧吧 哩啦哩吧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.87,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur3}吧吧吧吧 啦哩啦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.87,0:21:37.42,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur3}吧吧吧吧 哩啦哩吧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:39.79,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur3}吧吧吧吧吧吧吧
